402911,37 - 15,39 = 40,2895,98  It looks like it's time to finish the running year ... Tomorrow the weather is rather under the dog and I think I will keep my strength for the new year, besides why annoy my wife on New Year's Eve? (͡º ͜ʖ͡º)  I was supposed to run yesterday, but when I took out my nose from the garage, the delicate cabbage turned into a regular downpour and I decided that I did not care so much, because the forecasts for the next day were better.  Today I overslept a bit - I was going to start at 6 o'clock, still before dawn ... but how to after the cinema (Green Book - DIVINE FILM, I recommend) goes to zapieksy in a roundabout, returns home at midnight and takes away for mulled wine ... this getting up before 6 medium comes out ¯ \ _ (ツ) _ / ¯ So I did not start until 7:45, just after the sunrise, which - surprisingly - was even visible for a moment. After this moment, the sky became gray again and it remained so until the end of the race. Fortunately, the forecasts came true perfectly - 2 ° C above zero, strong wind and heavily reduced smog, no rain. Only somehow there was a lack of enthusiasm ... but since I was already outside it was necessary to use, I chose the route 14k with an additional kilometer tongue (͡ ° ͜ʖ ͡ °)  Again the start was bad - so weak that I almost decided to calm the trot ... but some hope came back on the third kilometer, I accelerated from the hill and - to my own surprise - not only kept the pace, but also did not let me overcome the hill and I slowed only slightly at the run. Then one more flattening, sprinting down ... and suddenly there was hope of breaking 5:00 / km! Nothing but finger injury (I still feel this navicular in some shoes) already approaching 5:00 was a success ... and it succeeded - nice accent at the end of the year, 4:58 min / km ᕙ (⇀‸↼ " ) ᕗ  The year was successful, for the second year in a row exceeded 3000 km, the pace may not be any killing but bearable ... I wish you Mirki and Mirabelki all the best in the coming year! Good luck running and more! #inteligencja #zdrowie #medycyna #psychologia #smog  http://maxmania.pl/nauka/zanieczyszczenia-powietrza-a-inteligencja-oglupia-nas-smog/  Air pollution and intelligence: How smog makes us stupid  The fact that impurities negatively affect physical health is a well-known fact. It may be disturbing, however, the discovery that impurities in the air also affect the state of our minds. Can contaminated air contribute to the decline in intelligence? It turns out that this way: as research conducted in China shows, air pollution is a factor that has a significant impact on our mental fitness. To test the relationship between air purity and mental decline, Chinese researchers turned to China Family Panel Studies, which regularly conducts specific intelligence tests among the population of this country. This organization provided the researchers with the results of tests carried out on up to 20,000 people. The researchers then checked the difference between the results over four years and then compared them to the level of pollution in the provinces they came from. The results give food for thought. As one of the authors of the Xi Chen study explains, "air pollution can make us go back in education one year back." He also warns that this problem applies especially to the elderly and people whose educational level is less than the average. In such cases, the drop in the level of education can be even several times greater. This discovery is so disturbing that researchers do not know what exactly causes the decline in brain function. As the "main suspect", the so-called a white substance on which air pollution can have a particularly negative effect. However, to confirm this, further research will be needed. . show the whole source: budujemydom.pl   +: billiard, Majronn

The only ones punished with the DIESELGATE scandal in Poland? An association that fights Volkswagen!  For the first time we reveal this information - and we count on Wykop Efekt in the interest of all of us. Because if someone thinks that you can fight for justice in Poland and punish a dishonest company that admits mass deception and produce cars that poison our air en masse, it is very wrong.  Three years after the outbreak of the scandal, the only one punished is ... our association:  1. The District Court in Warsaw dismissed the class action and ordered StopVW to pay almost PLN 100,000 to Volkswagen in a bizarre verdict! @AloesPolska: Wrinkles? Not as horrible as it seems - there are ways. Change your lifestyle, change your mood and look!  Wrinkles are folds and skin deformations that appear as you age. Over the years, the skin loses elasticity, resulting in lines or small scratches that later become wrinkled text. Causes: When we age, sweat and sebaceous glands that provide the skin with moisture and fat, wear out and gradually stop working. This causes the skin to lose its elasticity and humidity. As a result, it becomes dry and breaks appear on it. It also starts to lose collagen, which keeps the skin of the face and body in good condition. Lack of collagen results in flaccid tissue, double chins, wrinkles around the neck, around the mouth, around the eyes ("crow's feet"), bags under the eyes etc. Destruction of collagen and other tissues is caused by the presence of free radicals, mainly produced by the sun, smog and adverse environmental impact.  The main causes of wrinkles  - no humidity (dehydration) - the creation of free radicals that oxidize tissues under the influence of sunlight (UV) strongest between 11:00 and 15:00 -smog and dry, destructive environment -mask face - wrinkles also causes a rough surface of the pillowcase - no vitamins A, B, C, E and minerals. Suggested supplementation and what to change in a lifestyle to improve the condition of our skin ?:  - avoid excessive tanning; according to Dr. Stephen Kurtin, this is the best way to prevent wrinkles - protect the face with creams with sunscreen - wear sunglasses with large lenses to prevent rays falling on the skin around the eyes -pow large amounts of water, as well as aloe juice to moisturize the skin -take multiminerals and vitamins A, B, C and E. Beta-carotene (provitamin A) and vitamins C, E are very effective in neutralizing free radicals - use soft fiber cushions or sleep supine; try to avoid mimic contractions; - Massage each face gently for about 2 minutes to stimulate circulation -use moisturizing creams - the reason for the deterioration of the skin condition is seen in the reduction of certain hormones involved in the transport of fats to the cells by the appropriate glands. This causes a loss of balance of these fats partly due to the presence of free radicals in cells, glands and tissues throughout the body. -Release and change the skin! - Do not smoke - they damage the radiant appearance of the skin and affect the color of the teeth  PEELING (removal of the top layer of the skin) There are substances like phenol and its derivatives that are used to remove or remove the top layer of the skin (damaged and wrinkled). This supplementation in most cases causes a complete change of skin on the face, eliminating or reducing wrinkles and scars. It can cause skin blemishes. There are also less harmful substances that slower remove the top layer of the skin, e.g. retinol and retin-A. This product is also effective in the fight against acne. The results of this treatment come slower, but it is safer.  AHA Alpha-hydroxy acids Currently, other series of chemical exfoliants (peeling) and strong irrigation agents such as alpha-hydroxy acids have been discovered. These acids are combined (depending on the manufacturer) with other ingredients, e.g. Aloe vera, to obtain a different characteristic. An example of such an acid type is glycolic acid. These products remove dead epidermal cells and hydrate the skin. With constant use, they make big changes in the appearance of the skin, renewing and rejuvenating it. The best products are made of acids from natural sources such as fruits. The best combination is the combination of these acids with the aloe pulp, because the aloe penetrates deeply rebuilding the skin cells and eliminating possible irritations. At night I did not sleep because I could not fall asleep so I went to bed at 19:00 and woke up at 21:50. I had a nice dream, which I remembered very carefully. Well, I'm riding a bicycle to work in the morning and in the yard of the last house on the right before the bend I see something colorful. It had strange shapes. I did not have time to look at it, and besides it was far away so I go on. Around the bend, I see a thick, light-gray smoke fly from the chimney of this house, and it falls straight down onto the road in front of me, where it rolls around on the road. The smoke was strange, it had a homogeneous, light gray color, something like soiled milk and it did not mix with the air. The closer I was, the sharper the stench I felt. Something like a stench of burning plastic multiplied by ten glue or solvent mixed with stench. I think that if I eat this smoke I will not leave because even if it is not poisonous and I was sure it is, I will simply suffocate because it was thick and not mixed with the air. So I turned back, put my bike on the fence and crossed the gate to tell the mob that if they did not stop smoking so soon, I would call the police. I look, and there is Korwin with a white suit and hat behind the corner of the house, and the frightened marriage of some old men holding hands behind him. Outraged Korwin said loudly: "You can smoke things in a furnace with various things, but that's an exaggeration! I have small children and you poison the air!" Being in the yard, I could take a closer look at this colorful something. It looked like colored coal with longitudinal shapes. I thought it was probably a pile of leftists. After a while, the police arrived, cheery policemen saw what and how immediately they fixed the mandate 700 zloties to the elderly and the second wanted to glue Korwinowi, not really known for what. I guess that he did not call the police right away, he only went to spoil the stinks first. Korwin said that he could afford to pay the ticket but he would not be able to pay such an unfair mandate and would not accept him, let him be locked up in prison. After a while, the second police car arrived and the police jointly announced that they would call the boss, let him worry. The boss came, but Korwin did not want to accept the ticket from him either. Well, the boss called his boss, then the head of the boss called the next boss, etc. Finally stood in front of the house with ten police cars and blocked the road, which in the meantime from the rural, local road became an arrow straight on the highway and the winter turned into spring (I think that this presence of Corvinus affected the acceleration of economic growth and global warming). A multi-kilometer long queue took place on the highway, and the debating police officers advised that they would call Jasia. I went to the side of the highway and when I left about a kilometer I noticed that the driver of a truck taking advantage of the opportunity crashes into the ditch these strange rainbow lumps. I ran back to the police to inform them of littering, but nobody paid any attention to me. After a moment, Jaś came. He was short, about forty, and his heavily tanned and wind-dried skin was a body full of tense muscles and tendons. On his face he had glasses like Sylwester Stallone in the movie "Cobra" and looked like general Polko. When Korwin saw him, he froze for a moment and then he shouted: "Hansel ?! But you grew up, I have not seen you for centuries." It turned out that Jaś was a neighbor of Korwin, who for a kid went fishing with him and then became a commando and a policeman. Jaś listened to what was going on and told everyone to go home. End.  #korwin #sen #smog show the whole   +: Rennie-
